author: andreasmyth
msg: Changed text of warnings to inform user that application continues using default configuration

This is the case when using a malformed url, no resource exists at  the given url, the config file has an error (e.g. invalid xml), or contains definitions for beans of a class that is not on the classpath.

Implemented accessors to Executor in ServiceImpl and used executor - when specified - to execute the asynchronous tasks. Needed to change the ClientBinding and ClientTransport interfaces for that purpose.
